## âš™ï¸ Run the Demo

### 1. Create and Activate a Virtual Environment
```bash
python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate   # Mac/Linux
venv\Scripts\activate      # Windows
````

### 2. Install Dependencies

```bash
pip install flask
```

### 3. Start the Server

```bash
python app.py
```

Visit in browser:
ğŸ‘‰ `http://127.0.0.1:5000/`

