## ğŸ“¡ Demo API Endpoints

The backend provides mock API endpoints for demonstration purposes:

* `GET /api/ongoing` â†’ Returns ongoing productions (hardcoded list)
* `GET /api/history` â†’ Returns production history (hardcoded list)
* `POST /api/production` â†’ Adds a new production (temporary, in memory only)

---

## ğŸ›  Technologies

* **Frontend:** React (CDN), TailwindCSS, Feather Icons
* **Backend:** Flask (demo with in-memory data)

